Class SingleUseMockAccumuloStore

  • public class SingleUseMockAccumuloStore
extends MockAccumuloStore
    An AccumuloStore that uses an Accumulo MockInstance to provide a Connector. For the SingleUseMockAccumuloStore each time initialise is called the underlying table as set in the store properties is deleted.
